  "original_title": "\u0db8\u0dd4\u0daf\u0dbd\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dd9\u0db1 \u0da7\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0da7\u0dca \u0db1\u0ddc\u0daf\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dca \u0dbd\u0d82\u0d9c\u0db8 \u0d9a\u0ddc\u0db1\u0dca\u0daf\u0ddc\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dad\u0dbb\u0dc0\u0dbb\u0dd4 3\u0d9a\u0da7 \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0da9\u0dc0\u0dbb\u0daf\u0dd3",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "On duty for 3 Langama conductors who did not take money and give tickets",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A senior official of the Ceylon Transportation Board said that the services of three conductors of the Ceylon Traffic Board (Langama) who did not issue tickets after taking money from passengers are to be suspended.",
        "The officer mentioned that three conductors of two buses on the expressway from Monaragala to Makumbura and Galle to Kadawata and a regular service bus from Tangalle to Embilipitiya have been accused of taking money and not issuing tickets. did",
        "The official said that during the operation, it was found that tickets worth 2,190 rupees on the bus from Monaragala to Makumbura, 9 tickets worth 1,190 rupees on the bus from Galle to Kadawata and 5 tickets on the bus from Tangalle to Ambilipitiya had not been given. He also mentioned that legal proceedings are being taken against the conductors of the buses.",
        "A team led by Mr. Washington Rajapaksa, chief mobile inspector of the Ceylon Transport Board, implemented this operation."
      ],
